{"tid":2353951,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"客貨車衝入理大校園 兩人受傷","createTime":"2021-01-05T06:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T09:20:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a66eaf9034cf0221a472c30851712d47050fc894","tid":2353951,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一輛客貨車懷疑失控衝入理工大學校園，車上兩人受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n出事客貨車撞毀漆威道南一列水馬及圍欄後，衝了入理工大學泳池旁邊一條小徑，警方事後將行人路封閉。<br />\n<br />\n中午約十二時，客貨車沿漆威道南行駛至理工大學時，懷疑失控，車上兩人受輕傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=419090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419090&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=9d9d8776\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419090&h=cbc21cbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=419090</a>"},{"pid":"b14568b5c4c513832aac8bba01dd23066f9daa97","tid":2353951,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c49be7fcdc39ab7de21c08b802c1c85efd9a182","tid":2353951,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d173a580c56e98148b06120366815261d0214e","tid":2353951,"uid":233316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:41:24.000Z","msg":"搭錯時光機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107f5128f1b1793a1a69fea4f9b92a91455d7a90","tid":2353951,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"撞死力架沒？"},{"pid"